{"tid":1786820,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不如幫班黑警, 正名叫\"畜牲\"","createTime":"2019-12-17T12:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T05:02:46.000Z","uid":76310,"like":110,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"33ccca4369d6598905138d5d5a51e1126f84d8ac","tid":1786820,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:13:56.000Z","msg":"不如幫班黑警, 正名叫&quot;畜牲&quot;, 咪再跟人叫曱甴<br />\n人地稱呼我地做曱甴, 我地跟人地既稱呼, 除左顯得詞窮外, 仲會混亂左自己友<br />\n有人叫曱甴, 究竟係話邊個?<br />\n<br />\n畜牲, 比人圈養, 主子叫佢點就點, 完全無自己思想, 同魔警一樣<br />\n畜牲, 得個空殼存在, 食, 訓同住, 完全和班魔警一樣<br />\n畜牲, 當然沒有道德是非觀念, 主子叫佢做乜就做乜, 完全和班魔警一樣<br />\n畜牲呢個字, 其實好適合班魔警"},{"pid":"c5c7d3177ecc128248f7e48705e255762a8e9e1e","tid":1786820,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bf72f9fdf703b1f5e929ef914c413998c8ae4d","tid":1786820,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f99fbc6eb4b232e4c558bce9831d1a2c1b56fc","tid":1786820,"uid":327462,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:17:50.000Z","msg":"唔好悔辱畜牲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用任何一個詞語都形容唔到呢班object<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2cb9e6f5d19a1962b2d4edef18380f847305c9","tid":1786820,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38537539da7fd185303a78376f11ca884cd0d10a","tid":1786820,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":