, 主子叫佢點就點, 完全無自己思想, 同魔警一樣<br />\n畜牲, 得個空殼存在, 食, 訓同住, 完全和班魔警一樣<br />\n畜牲, 當然沒有道德是非觀念, 主子叫佢做乜就做乜, 完全和班魔警一樣<br />\n畜牲呢個字, 其實好適合班魔警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:19:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d806924b11a3b911ece4cf62f182e38a40e01e4","tid":1786820,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>賤種</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">未上前線全家均遭起底 妻子遭騷擾 bb被罵小賤種 總督察譚汝禧：不會退縮，事件加強自己止暴製亂，回復法治決心<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1788173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1788173</a></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"a05dbe67d127ac3f60ae4a9f716fc4426a4d1797","tid":1786820,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3823493667c176e8f67c7f5b2ef83ffcd1cb3ff5","tid":1786820,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"叫狗閪<br />\n<br />\n叉雞飯呀叔教既"},{"pid":"f758be0ff4a9acf1b32059314d8be46a628a2819","tid":1786820,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d87d54816ac5bb45ec1760a85163cd289a8cca","tid":1786820,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"畜牲"},{"pid":"9682c67d79707377eeebebf167c0e65d437f8d70","tid":1786820,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:22:11.000Z","msg":"畜牲"},{"pid":"616b0a5d7bcfc879bfab01377321e4e119d311fe","tid":1786820,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:23:21.000Z","msg":"佢地先係曱甴"},{"pid":"9000336d584dbd0705bfdadf939f22a8f33767df","tid":1786820,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:24:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d258f971fa4be51ddc01cd308ca35b55ee21a50c","tid":1786820,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"有一句說話包可以令曱甴警發火，就係「有爺生無乸教」，包佢衝來打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056abcfebfbbba49adedb30362527f7d8c7c3942","tid":1786820,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:27:58.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n叫佢地甚至叫藍屍做曱甴<br />\n就係專登混淆<br />\n咩叫自己人好亂<br />\n你自己中意比人叫曱甴係你事<br />\n我地唔中意<br />\n<br />\n實測藍曱甴比我叫曱甴好大反應<br />\n好想開我拖<br />\n應該覺得好大侮辱<br />\n明明平時叫開人曱甴<br />\n但竟然比人叫番轉頭<br />\n呢個正正係我地想要既效果"},{"pid":"6b764e81cfbc10cb9fec2a7d888f7fcc86ba7426","tid":1786820,"uid":87735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:30:21.000Z","msg":"涷牲"},{"pid":"a439a1028e8327ffe5b124ad6b322b361629bc24","tid":1786820,"uid":316507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"折J哥布林"},{"pid":"41584ab0a2735fffade2dbaf3ce67836f955a844","tid":1786820,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"其實我一直都唔明語言攻擊有咩意義? 班黑警喺學堂應該聽一啲更惡毒嘅語句聽到慣哂, 你大聲咁叫佢反而會令佢即刻揾把槍指住佢. 反而我覺得大家應該喺黑警面前表現得友善啲, 然後近距離攻擊"},{"pid":"60848a3d5dc58471aa12482a1055d888d090c6ee","tid":1786820,"uid":51364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:22:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲叫開佢地做殺人犯"},{"pid":"bfc0511c9e007954fd8bb9a820d02c00311ed062","tid":1786820,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"上次屯門公園佢哋話麻木晒啦，任得你哋點講喎，既然麻木晒咁我以後叫你哋做<br />\n【屌你老母】<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce98c3e11a9c1d8f91bd22e43b04c43d7f6e195b","tid":1786820,"uid":60868,"like":